Class ProjectsFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v4.app.Fragment
      • com.matchid.matchidapplicatie.ProjectsFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.content.ComponentCallbacks, android.view.View.OnCreateContextMenuListener

    public class ProjectsFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
    A simple Fragment subclass. Activities that contain this fragment must implement the ProjectsFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener interface to handle interaction events. Use the newInstance() factory method to create an instance of this fragment.
